        "content": "<p>For a project, I need to use that the symmetric group admits a presentation by generators and relations of the form : <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=\"fraktur\">S</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>≅</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">⟨</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow></msub><mspace width=\"1em\"/><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.36em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><msubsup><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>e</mi></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>j</mi></msub></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mo lspace=\"0em\" rspace=\"0em\">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i